comments[7]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-08T23:20:45.388Z",codex-audit,"Duplicate-check evidence: ran pm context --limit 10,pm search dogfood audit telemetry sentry semantic search SDK calendar extensibility CI --limit 10,pm list-in-progress --limit 20,pm list-open --limit 20,and pm search 2026-05-08 2026-05-09 latest-build temp-project dogfood audit remediate --limit 10. Found open parent feature pm-rnpb and only closed prior execution tasks,so this dated execution task is required without duplicating parent scope."
  "2026-05-08T23:21:03.597Z",codex-audit,"Started latest-build audit. Bootstrap passed: npm install -g ., pm --version 2026.5.6, node v25.9.0, pnpm 10.33.0, pnpm build passed."
  "2026-05-08T23:22:52.929Z",codex-audit,"Dogfood finding: initial temp script tried unsupported init/config flags and pm returned structured, actionable unknown-option/tracker-not-initialized guidance. Rerunning with strict set -e and supported commands for clean evidence."
  "2026-05-08T23:24:04.190Z",codex-audit,"Dogfood finding: strict temp run confirmed extension scaffold/install/doctor/ping works, but also showed agents must not assume sequential item IDs. pm generated random IDs and parent mutation warned on a guessed pm-0002 parent, so the next run uses --json plus jq ID capture."
  "2026-05-09T00:19:55.795Z",codex-audit,"Evidence: temp dogfood lifecycle passed at /tmp/pm-cli-dogfood-json-2reGLF with extension init/install/doctor/ping, create/claim/update/append/comments/notes/learnings/files/docs/test/list/context/calendar/search/reindex keyword/health/validate/test-run/close/release. Semantic smoke passed at /tmp/pm-cli-semantic-smoke-lsx8RU with local Ollama/Qwen hybrid reindex and semantic search. Full repository forced hybrid reindex was stopped after remaining CPU-bound on 679 items; health reports no stale vectors, and Sentry PM-CLI-9 drove the payload-cap/adaptive-split fix."
  "2026-05-09T00:20:38.871Z",codex-audit,"Verification evidence: focused tests passed for embedding-batches/reindex/test/test-all and release-readiness-runtime; pnpm typecheck passed; pnpm build passed; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed 1219/1219 with 100% statements/branches/functions/lines; pnpm quality:static passed; node scripts/check-secrets.mjs passed; npm pack --dry-run passed; pnpm smoke:npx passed; compatibility-check.mjs --json passed; pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift passed; pm health --check-only reports ok with Ollama + LanceDB active and zero stale vectors."
  "2026-05-09T10:48:59.847Z",codex-audit,"CI follow-up: Windows Node 20 failed tests/unit/reindex-command.spec.ts because the truncation regression passed a 50k body through a CLI argument. Reduced the fixture body to 1k characters, which still exceeds the semantic 200-character truncation cap and avoids Windows command-line limits. Verification: PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/reindex-command.spec.ts passed 10/10; node scripts/check-secrets.mjs passed; git diff --check passed."
